        <div class="msgSubject">leveling from 1-10 Goldsmith</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-09-20 16:34:02 | Edited: Sep 21 2010  9:30am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1285022042170591050" id="quote-1285022042170591050" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1285022042170591050" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=194&amp;mid=1285022042170591050&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1285022042170591050&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1285022042170591050" onclick="followToggle('add','1285022042170591050')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
